{2000}{}{[The man is sitting behind his desk filling out reports, and drinking Rotgut. He tips his fedora as you approach] Citizen.}
{2010}{}{I think the day is safe again, enough to make Lady Justice blush.}
{2020}{}{Another day, Detective. Another call to answer.}
{2030}{}{Who are you?}
{2040}{}{I'm...}
