{25000}{}{[You and the Detective walk around the poorest part of town, but it really isn't that bad. You've seen far worse poverty before, these people don't know how good they have it here in the NCR]}
{25010}{}{[Continue your patrol]}
{25020}{}{[Continue your patrol]}
